ID: Changes to this doc can break the nose tests or interfere with test systems!  BEFORE making changes, please read https://confluence.oceanobservatories.org/display/CIDev/Preload+development.  AFTER making changes, please TEST, make a copy of this sheet, and commit the new URL to ion_loader.py!

input_resource_id: The resource to be linked to - link assocuation depends on value in column resource_type
source_resource_id: Additionally, association of type hasSource from DataProduct to an InstrumentDevice or PlatformDevice.
resource_type: Type of input_resource_id (behavior will be different for different types)

comment: link data product to external dataset
